### Escalate Within 4 Hours
- Complex inquiries beyond standard responses
- Requests for executive meetings
- Partnership or vendor negotiations

### Handle Independently
- Routine email inquiries
- Meeting scheduling
- Standard information requests
- Calendar management
- Follow-up reminders

